These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, indie, rock, soul
House: gothic-revival, victorian, cottage, tower
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, ritmeester, dannemann, game
1. the fan of indie is on the right of the game-smoker##1
2. the game-smoker is between the victorian house and the fan of folk##2
3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the fan of rock##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
6. the cottage house is on the right of the fan of indie##1
7. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | folk    | rock      | indie      | soul    |
| House   | tower | gothic-revival | victorian | cottage |
| Cigar     | ritmeester    | game       | dannemann     | bongani     |

