.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, corn, cucumber, peach
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, daffodil, lily, bellflower
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, bartender, teacher, fisherman
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left##1
2. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating peach##1
3. the teacher is on the left of the person eating corn##1
4. the fisherman is on the far left##1
5. the fisherman is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
6. the software-developer is on the right of the person eating corn##1
7. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| Food          | avocado     | peach     | corn       | cucumber    |
| Flower         | daffodil | lily   | azalea | bellflower |
| Job   | fisherman    | teacher | bartender    | software-developer        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, camping, board-games, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, disaster, superhero, mystery
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, cycling, sailing
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Hobby      | photography | camping  | board-games    | video-games |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | mystery  | thriller  | disaster    |
| Sport         | climbing    | sailing | baseball | cycling  |

