.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-4::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, broccoli, kiwi, pineapple
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, ivory, white, green
4 different games are played: scrabble, canasta, go, bridge
1. the person playing canasta is between the person who likes ivory and the person eating avocado##2
2. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
3. the person playing go is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
4. the person eating kiwi is on the far left##1
5. the person playing scrabble is the person eating pineapple##1
6. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
7. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
8. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Food          | kiwi   | avocado     | broccoli | pineapple |
| Color   | white | green | lilac   | ivory     |
| Game           | bridge | go      | canasta     | scrabble       |

