.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-5::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, kiwi, mango, raspberry
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, begonia, tulip, balloon-flower
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, reggae, trance, hip-hop
1. the person eating eggplant is on the far right##1
2. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
3. the person who growstulip is the fan of funk##1
4. the person who growsrose is between the person eating mango and the person eating kiwi##2
5. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
6. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
7. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
8. the person eating mango is the fan of trance##1
9. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | mango      | raspberry | kiwi      | eggplant |
| Flower           | begonia | rose | balloon-flower | tulip   |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | hip-hop   | reggae     | funk   |

