.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, entrepreneur, videographer
City: miami, nizza, hamburg, colone
4 different games are played: backgammon, snooker, chess, monopoly
1. the person playing snooker is the coach##1
2. the person playing chess is the person traveling to colone##1
3. the coach is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
5. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
6. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
7. the doctor is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
8. the doctor is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Job           | coach    | doctor   | entrepreneur | videographer |
| City   | miami     | hamburg   | colone         | nizza        |
| Game         | snooker | backgammon | chess         | monopoly       |

