.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, gardening, traveling, writing
City: paris, venice, boston, san-francisco
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, january, april, march
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 4. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 7. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
10. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
11. the person traveling to venice is the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby         | traveling    | camping  | gardening | writing   |
| City           | san-francisco | venice   | boston    | paris |
| Birthday   | march      | april | january | november  |

