.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-8::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, azalea, zinnia, balloon-flower
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, hip-hop, gospel, indie
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, mystery, spy, western
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
2. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
4. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
6. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
7. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
8. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
| Flower          | zinnia | azalea    | balloon-flower | aconite    |
| Music-Genre         | gospel     | indie | hip-hop  | d&b |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery    | western      | action   | spy         |

