.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite, tea, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, singing, dancing, traveling
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, quad-bike, boat, ship
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
5. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
8. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | sprite    | tea            | water     | fanta      |
| Hobby           | reading    | traveling | dancing     | singing |
| Transport   | van | boat    | quad-bike | ship    |

