.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-10::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, train, trike, boat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, horror, thriller
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, skydiving, filmmaking, puzzles
1. the person watching horror movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
4. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is the person driving the boat##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
7. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
8. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Transport          | train   | trike | ship | boat |
| Movie-Genre   | horror   | crime     | action      | thriller  |
| Hobby   | gardening | skydiving   | filmmaking    | puzzles   |

