.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, lawyer, pilot, software-developer
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, rock-climbing, collecting, filmmaking
4 different games are played: whist, canasta, backgammon, scrabble
1. the lawyer is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the pilot is on the right of the engineer##1
5. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person playing whist##1
8. the person playing whist is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2       |     3      |   4    |
| Job           | software-developer | lawyer        | engineer   | pilot  |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing             | chess     | filmmaking | collecting  |
| Game         | canasta           | scrabble | whist   | backgammon |

