.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, surfing, parkour, volleyball
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, grapefruit, zucchini, papaya
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, skateboard, snowmobile
1. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
6. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the helicopter and the person who's sport is surfing##2
7. the person who's sport is baseball is the person eating grapefruit##1
8. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Sport    | baseball   | parkour   | surfing    | volleyball |
| Food         | grapefruit | zucchini    | strawberry      | papaya |
| Transport   | helicopter      | snowmobile | skateboard | bike   |

