The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, freelancer, software-developer, dancer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, martial-arts, western, fantasy
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the scientist is between the person drinking coffee and the dancer##2
3. the freelancer is the person watching fantasy movies##1
4. the scientist is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
5. the freelancer is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
6. the person drinking coffee is the software-developer##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
8. the software-developer is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the person watching western movies is the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | coffee      | almond-milk | milk       | iced-tea  |
| Job       | software-developer | scientist | dancer    | freelancer |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts     | thriller         | western | fantasy     |

