The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, fisherman, scientist, software-developer
4 different games are played: snooker, chess, backgammon, domino
1. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is the firefighter##1
3. the software-developer is on the far left or far right##3
4. the software-developer is on the left of the person playing domino##1
5. the fisherman is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
6. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person playing domino##1
7. the owner of the turtle is the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Pet          | chinchilla          | rabbit     | ferret   | turtle   |
| Job           | software-developer | firefighter | fisherman | scientist |
| Game   | chess          | domino | backgammon   | snooker |

