The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, january, may, december
1. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the person eating cucumber is the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person eating cranberry is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating cherry is the owner of the goat##1
6. the person eating raspberry is between the person eating cherry and the person who's birthday is in january##2
7. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | cucumber | cherry    | raspberry | cranberry |
| Pet   | pony  | goat    | goldfish      | cat     |
| Birthday     | february | may | december   | january      |

