.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, juice, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, surfing, basketball, rowing
There 4 different types of food: garlic, cauliflower, strawberry, spinach
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking coffee is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
4. the person eating cauliflower is between the person eating garlic and the person eating strawberry##2
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1
7. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
8. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4      |
