3. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
4. the person watching action movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person playing snooker is between the person who likes lavender and the person playing billiard##2
6. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1
7. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |   3   |   4    |
| Game      | billiard      | snooker     | bridge | go |
| Movie-Genre   | musical    | fantasy    | spy   | action |
| Color     | red | ebony | lavender   | coral    |

