.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-19::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, turtle, rat, horse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, jazz, salsa, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, indian, malaysian, russian
1. the russian is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the russian##3
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
4. the argentine is on the far left or far right##3
5. the indian is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
6. the fan of trance is on the left of the argentine##1
7. the owner of the turtle is the malaysian##1
8. the fan of classical is between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the guinea-pig##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Pet      | turtle | horse    | guinea-pig | rat  |
| Music-Genre          | jazz          | classical | trance       | salsa      |
| Nationality   | malaysian     | indian    | russian     | argentine |

