.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, azalea, daffodil, zinnia
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, journalist, security-guard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, soul, dubstep, electronic
1. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
2. the fan of soul is on the right of the bartender##1
3. the fan of dubstep is the person who growszinnia##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
5. the fan of soul is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who growsdaffodil##2
6. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
7. the fan of dubstep is on the far right##1
8. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the journalist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| Flower    | daffodil | azalea  | marigold  | zinnia           |
| Job     | bartender | journalist | dancer   | security-guard |
| Music-Genre   | electronic   | soul       | pop | dubstep  |

 